{"tid":525093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再度發生王寶強事件 PG ONE笠人綠帽","createTime":"2018-01-10T09:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T11:43:14.000Z","uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75b1e398267753b6931ad797959deee7a82cc503","tid":525093,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"李小璐和PG ONE先後兩次被曝出一些不當的行為，最開始李小璐被曝夜宿PG ONE的家中，後面PG ONE搭車去李小璐家<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172250_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172250_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=eb3fe338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大除夕當日，李小璐和PG One被內地爆出在上月底在男方住所度通宵，更有翹手等親密動作。在內地演藝界有「寵妻狂魔」之稱的賈乃亮隨即發文指「了解璐璐為人，也信任我所有的朋友，我相信一切都很美好！」替李小璐及PG One護航，當晚夫妻更合體現身跨年騷曬恩愛！李小璐則解釋有其他朋友包括馬蘇等為電影在男方住所開會外，PG One亦發文以「哥嫂」稱呼賈乃亮和李小璐，指他們待自己猶如親弟！<br />\n雖然賈乃亮一開始也選擇相信老婆，但他本人似乎不知道當天李小璐出門是與姊妹聚會，更不曉得PG ONE也在席間，結果6日晚間事情忽然出現大翻轉，賈乃亮在《微博》貼出一篇千字長文，字字句句充滿無奈與痛苦，「對不起璐璐，也許，還是我做的不夠好」，同時也取消關注PG ONE，刪除所有兩人以前稱兄道弟的合照，正式與他絕交。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172158_83f12c87f884ac277ed971b247cd15f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172158_83f12c87f884ac277ed971b247cd15f3.jpg&h=86191cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172210_ae2d7d7d3e63b285ab0bc51aaf485ea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172210_ae2d7d7d3e63b285ab0bc51aaf485ea7.jpg&h=6d61d26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好地地一家三口<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172230_c12ea209963cee8e72e411e71ae427c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172230_c12ea209963cee8e72e411e71ae427c0.jpg&h=f4ee8327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸女星李小璐「不雅」影片流出　聲紋比對後竟似本人？！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172306_695e721f70b78df420fa4759739fb193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172306_695e721f70b78df420fa4759739fb193.jpg&h=656ebb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n系唔系真就唔知<br />\n自己估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172129_77ce81a9763c3f314d2e31533e7bebdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172129_77ce81a9763c3f314d2e31533e7bebdf.jpg&h=41ae2d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n枉佢老公咁愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">G</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"0a76cbe1753cc31a4fcf4fb628a832f55ef0cda0","tid":525093,"uid":143336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"476eb6a5a10d9f8210b35f141d88989348b1bb3d","tid":525093,"uid":143336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bfb083d8d718be9c2df2839cfe3ff80e5bc517f7","tid":525093,"uid":52299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"冇左最重要果樣野 點討論"},{"pid":"a4877b8cd571c8ca2a3c4278697213114e0a778e","tid":525093,"uid":42487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"RAP得勁, 條脷係咪郁得好似摩打咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4ab8860f661bfc060cb567ac991c2f79c0e3fe","tid":525093,"uid":120764,"like":1,"